original_title: Ayumi Hamasaki: A Museum, 30th single collection live
overview: A MUSEUM ~30th single collection live~ is a concert DVD from Hamasaki Ayumi. it features a wide variety of her songs from early in her career, up to her latest releases (at the time). It also features a collection of unique costumes including a dress made of roses and a wedding dress with a very long veil.
title: Ayumi Hamasaki: A Museum, 30th single collection live
